  "texts": [
    "The diversity and complexity of virtual and actual objects, contents, and human avatars necessitate the development of more flexible semantic segmentation approaches.",
    "The semantic segmentation algorithms must be able to tell the real pixels from the virtual ones, especially in the interlaced Metaverse world.",
    "In this situation, the class information may be more complex, and the semantic segmentation models may be required to work with classes that are not yet known.",
    "There are two types of object detection in the Metaverse: detection of unique instances (such as a face, marker, or text) and identification of general categories (such as automobiles and people).",
    "In XR, (Hbali et al. 2016; Nahuel et al. 2020), text detection techniques have been extensively researched."
  ],
